#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:1
msgid "Form Editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:3
msgid ""
"The Form Editor lets you create and edit **Camunda Forms** (schemaVersion "
"16) directly in the Linked Data Explorer. Forms authored here can be linked "
"to BPMN `UserTask` and `StartEvent` elements in the BPMN Modeler and "
"deployed to Operaton in a single operation alongside the process definition."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:12
msgid "Two-panel layout"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:14
msgid "The Form Editor uses a two-panel layout:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:16
msgid ""
"**Left panel** — Form list. Shows all forms stored in `localStorage` with "
"create, rename, and delete actions. An **EXAMPLE** badge marks the three "
"read-only seed forms; user-created forms carry a **WIP** badge."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:17
msgid ""
"**Right panel** — Form canvas. Hosts the `@bpmn-io/form-js` graphical editor "
"for the selected form, with a toolbar for saving and exporting."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:21
msgid "Form list panel"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:23
msgid ""
"The list panel shows every form in storage. Each entry displays the form "
"name, its schema ID, and a status badge."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:25
msgid "Badge"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:25
