msgid "**EXAMPLE**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:25
msgid "Read-only seed form — cannot be renamed or deleted"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:25
msgid "**WIP**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:25
msgid "User-created form — fully editable"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:30
msgid "Actions available on each form:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:32
msgid "**Click** — opens the form in the canvas editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:33
msgid "**Double-click name** — enters inline rename mode (WIP forms only)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:34
msgid "**Trash icon** — deletes the form after confirmation (WIP forms only)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:35
msgid ""
"**+ button** (header) — creates a new empty form with `schemaVersion 16`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:39
msgid "Example forms"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:41
msgid ""
"On first launch the application seeds three read-only example forms if "
"`localStorage` is empty. They demonstrate complete Camunda Form schemas and "
"serve as a starting point for customisation."
msgstr ""

