msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:51
msgid "Form canvas"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:53
msgid ""
"The canvas is a full `@bpmn-io/form-js` visual editor. A component palette "
"on the left of the canvas lets you drag fields, dropdowns, checkboxes, text "
"blocks, and buttons onto the form. The properties panel on the right of the "
"canvas edits the selected component's label, key, validation rules, and FEEL "
"conditions."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:55
msgid "The canvas toolbar provides:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:57
msgid ""
"**Save** — persists the current schema to `localStorage`. The button is "
"active only when unsaved changes exist."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:58
msgid ""
"**Export `.form`** — downloads the schema as a `.form` JSON file compatible "
"with Camunda Modeler and Operaton."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:59
msgid "**Close** — returns to the empty-state view."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:63
msgid "Storage"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:65
msgid ""
"Forms are stored in PostgreSQL via the LDE backend under the key "
"`linkedDataExplorer_formSchemas`, cached locally in `localStorage` for "
"instant synchronous access. On editor load, the service fetches the "
"authoritative list from `GET /v1/assets/forms` and replaces the local cache. "
"All schemas use:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:67
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"schemaVersion\": 16,\n"
"  \"executionPlatform\": \"Camunda Platform\",\n"
"  \"executionPlatformVersion\": \"7.21.0\"\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:75
msgid ""
"Example forms (`readonly: true`) are seeded from `public/examples/` and are "
"never written to the database."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:77
msgid "See [Asset Storage]{1} for the full architecture."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:81
msgid "Integration with the BPMN Modeler"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:83
msgid ""
"The Form Editor and BPMN Modeler share the same `FormService` storage layer. "
"A form saved in the Form Editor appears instantly in the **Link to Form** "
"dropdown when a `UserTask` or `StartEvent` is selected in the BPMN Modeler. "
"No page reload or manual sync step is required."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:85
msgid ""
"See [BPMN Modeler — Form linking]{1} and the [Form Editor user guide]{2} for "
"step-by-step instructions."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:89
msgid "Language and organization"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:91
msgid "The Form Editor footer panel mirrors the BPMN Modeler footer:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:93
msgid ""
"**Language** — ISO 639-1 dropdown (Language-agnostic / English / Dutch / "
"German). Persisted as the `language` column on `form_schemas`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:94
msgid ""
"**Organization** — free-text input with autocomplete from existing "
"organization keys. Persisted as the `organization` column."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:96
msgid ""
"Both live on the LDE `FormSchema` wrapper, not inside the form-js `schema` "
"object — the form-js spec stays unmodified."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:98
msgid ""
"The list panel toolbar offers free-text search and language filtering; forms "
"are grouped under collapsible organization headers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:100
msgid "Filename-based language inference on import"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:102
msgid ""
"A file named `<form-id>.<lang>.form` (e.g. `capacity-claim-intake.nl.form`) "
"is auto-tagged on import. Precedence:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:104
msgid "Top-level `language` key in the file's JSON (set by **Export .form**)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:105
msgid "Filename suffix `.<lang>.form`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:106
msgid "Untagged"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:108
msgid "Form export round-trip"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:110
msgid ""
"Clicking **Export .form** wraps the form-js schema with the active "
"`language` and `organization` at the top of the exported JSON and uses a "
"language-suffixed filename. Re-importing populates both fields automatically "
"— round-trip integrity preserved without extending the form-js schema spec. "
"The wrapper keys are stripped on import before the schema reaches form-js."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:112
msgid "Save button dirty tracking"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:114
msgid ""
"Pending-until-Save: the **Save** button starts disabled, enables on the "
"first canvas or footer edit, and disables again after a successful save. "
"Typing in the footer dropdowns does not regroup the form in the list until "
"you click Save."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:116
msgid "See [Multilingualism]{1} for the architectural overview."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:118
msgid "Known limitation — form-js properties panel focus loss"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:120
msgid ""
"The form-js properties panel loses input focus when typing pauses (Field "
"label, Description, Key). Upstream form-js issue #86, marked wontfix by bpmn-"
"io. Not LDE-caused, not fixable from React without forking form-js. "
"Workaround: edit the `.form` JSON in a code editor and re-import."
msgstr ""

